{"tid":933014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解美國司法部要強調孟有好多中港護照？好正常囉唔該","createTime":"2018-12-08T08:16:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-08T17:26:21.000Z","uid":15696,"like":1,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4f31543476705589a6c5804ec21aad2850cd80d9","tid":933014,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T08:16:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">孟晚舟至少曾持有7本中國或香港護照（4本中國3本香港），而這7本只是孟過去11年前往美國用過的護照，美國司法部認為她完全有可能還有其他護照，所以即使加拿大當局充公了她入境用的護照，她也有可能用其他方法潛逃。<br />\n<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>報失護照no都唔同啦！</strong>用二頁講佢有好多香港護照托柒咩！<br />\n<br />\n佢一定唔會有其他護照囉！美帝司法部一定係弱智！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd08ef571f3c3a10007a4ccf8c53d9cfd75f5575","tid":933014,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T08:17:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"589336e140fdeb80ef95741af9a06df4091724bc","tid":933014,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T08:19:47.000Z","msg":"真係好正常囉 我每次去日本旅行都用唔同護照嫁啦"},{"pid":"ca2c6a7c23a4744393f2e0ed292ea1a1295fbd56","tid":933014,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T08:20:46.000Z","msg":"因為做佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b7c0c2ce41f9e265c4e9aeec96ca2828e95fd7b","tid":933014,"uid":66242,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":